You misunderstand.  Serving others (in a religious sense) does not entail catering to the will of others.  Also, serving others outwardly while inwardly resenting it isn't really serving then is it?  <br>
<br>
No, I don't get tired of serving, I get downright pissed sometimes cause I'd rather sleep than go sing for the little kids at church cause my son was up all night screaming etc etc !!! <br>
